All our products are passed by our bust support test (measurement of the decrease in breast bounce when running) conducted in our laboratories. They are evaluated and given a rating from 1 (low support) to 5 (high support).

HOW WAS THIS CLASSIC PADDED RUNNING CROP TOP DESIGNED?
This sports crop top was designed for optimal comfort and bust protection:
Like all the KALENJI models:
* we don't use wires to avoid injury and compression of glands
* we minimise seams around the nipple to avoid chafing
* we choose fabrics which wick away perspiration, to optimise comfort but also avoid chafing.

WHAT TYPE OF CUP DOES THE CLASSIC PADDED RUNNING CROP TOP HAVE?
The classic padded running crop top has 2 flexible cups in which 2 padded shoulders are inserted. 
Our range also includes sports crop tops and bras with non-moulded cups like the classic running crop top (item reference 8501390).

CHOOSING THE RIGHT SIZE FOR THE CLASSIC PADDED CROP TOP

The S size is equivalent to sizes 75A, 75B and 70C.

A CROP TOP OR A BRA?
The classic padded crop top is available in sizes XS to XL and is recommended for sizes up to a C-cup.
